M-v     scroll-down-command (moves cursor up)
C-M-v   scroll-other-window
C-M-S-v scroll-other-window-down (well, up)
M->     end-of-buffer            (also C-END)
M-<     beginning-of-buffer      (also C-POS1)

C-d     delete-char (DEL)
M-d     delete-word (C-DEL)

